{[}Temperature, Humidity, Moisture, SoilType\_enc, CropType\_enc, N, K,
P{]}

│

▼

Load fertilizer\_recommendation.csv → Train
DecisionTreeClassifier(criterion=\textquotesingle gini\textquotesingle)

│

▼

Root Node: Best split on highest Gini Gain feature

├── Branch A: Further splits...

│ └── Leaf: "Urea"

├── Branch B: Further splits...

│ └── Leaf: "DAP"

└── Branch C: Further splits...

└── Leaf: "14-35-14"

│

▼

Output: Fertilizer name (e.g., "Urea", "DAP", "MOP", "14-35-14")
\end{quote}

