\paragraph{\texorpdfstring{\textbf{How It Works in
AGROPORTAL}}{How It Works in AGROPORTAL}}\label{how-it-works-in-agroportal-1}}

\begin{quote}
{[}One-time Offline Training --- ZDecision\_Tree\_Model.py{]}

Load preprocessed2.csv (300,000 rows, all-India crop data)

→ Encode: State, District, Season using LabelEncoder

→ build\_tree() → Recursively split on best Gini Gain

→ joblib.dump(tree, \textquotesingle filetest2.pkl\textquotesingle)

{[}Runtime Inference --- ZDecision\_Tree\_Model\_Call.py{]}

joblib.load(\textquotesingle filetest2.pkl\textquotesingle)

→ Input: {[}State\_encoded, District\_encoded, Season\_encoded{]}

→ classify(row, tree) → Leaf node

→ class\_distribution: \{Rice: 45\%, Maize: 30\%, Ragi: 25\%\}

→ Output: All crops with probabilities
\end{quote}

