▼

ColumnTransformer → Combined feature matrix

│

▼

Train RandomForestRegressor(n\_estimators=100, random\_state=42)

│

▼

User input → Same OHE transformation → Predict

│

▼

Output: Production in Quintals (rounded to 2 decimals)
\end{quote}

